---
---

<section id="contact" class="py-24 px-6 bg-[#141228]">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="fade-in">
      <div class="section-divider"></div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-12">함께 일하고 싶으신가요? 연락해 주세요!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5 mb-10">
      <!-- Email -->
      <a href="mailto:leecoding@example.com"
         class="contact-card rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-3 fade-in" data-delay="100">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-500 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
          ✉️
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Email</p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs mt-1">leecoding@example.com</p>
        </div>
        <span class="text-blue-400 text-xs font-medium mt-1">메일 보내기 →</span>
      </a>

      <!-- GitHub -->
      <a href="https://github.com/leecoding" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
         class="contact-card rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-3 fade-in" data-delay="200">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-green-400 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
          🐱
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">GitHub</p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs mt-1">github.com/leecoding</p>
        </div>
        <span class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-medium mt-1">프로필 보기 →</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="fade-in" data-delay="300">
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-5">또는 직접 메시지를 남겨주세요</p>
      <a href="mailto:leecoding@example.com"
         class="btn-glow inline-block text-white font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded-full text-sm">
        👋 안녕하세요, 이코딩님!
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
